According to the [http://wiki.openwrt.org/doku.php?id=oldwiki:unsupported OpenWrt wiki], this is a AR2317 based router with 2MB Flash and 8MB RAM. Per other sources, the FCC ID is TE7WR54XG (TP-LINK TL-WR541G) and it is shown in FCC docs as using a Micrel SPN801012 processor (Kendin KS8695?) and an Atheros single-chip solution.
Per the manual and supporting WiGLE data, the default SSID is '''RG54SE II'''.
